    },
    "shortDescription": "<p>You are surrounded by a soporific aroma that causes living creatures that begin their turn or end their movement within 5 feet of you to fall asleep for 1 minute. Creatures must save each time they begin their turn or end their movement within the <i>cloak of dreams</i>, even if they have previously saved against the effect. Sleeping creatures are helpless but can be awakened with a standard action or after being wounded.</p><p>Creatures with the scent special quality have a -4 penalty on their saves.</p>"
